title: Disney vows to help repeal 'Don't Say Gay' law, says Florida Gov. DeSantis shouldn't have signed it - CNBC
content: Disney vows to help repeal 'Don't Say Gay' law, says Florida Gov. DeSantis shouldn't have signed it  CNBC
description: Disney has vowed to help have Florida's HB 1557 law, which is known as the "Don't Say Gay" bill, repealed.
